en: This table provides metadata for the actual indicator available from %country_name statistics closest to the corresponding global SDG indicator. Please note that even when the global SDG indicator is fully available from %country_adjective statistics, this table should be consulted for information on national methodology and other %country_adjective-specific metadata information.
zh-Hans: 此表格所提供的真正指标中的元数据可从接近相对的全球可持续发展目标指标的国家统计数据获得。请注意：全球可持续发展目标指标完全可从国家统计数据获得，此表格资料皆只用作参阅国家方法论及其他国家的元数据用途。

en: This table provides information on metadata for SDG indicators as defined by the UN Statistical Commission. Complete global metadata is provided by the UN Statistics Division.
zh-Hans: 此表格提供的资料是由联合国统计委员会所界定的可持续发展目标指标的元数据。完整的全球元数据是由联合国统计司提供的。

en: Click on each goal, or %before_link search, %after_link for %name statistics for Sustainable Development Goal global indicators.
zh-Hans: 点击每一个目标查询或自行%before_link搜索%after_link各个国家的可持续发展目标全球指标统计。

en: %name data for Sustainable Development Goal indicators
zh-Hans: %name可持续发展目标指标的数据

en: The Sustainable Development Goals (SDGs) are a universal call to action to end poverty, protect the planet and improve the lives and prospects of everyone, everywhere. The 17 Goals were adopted by all UN Member States in 2015, as part of the 2030 Agenda for Sustainable Development.
zh-Hans: 可持续发展目标是消除贫困，保护地球和 改善世界各地每个人的生活和前景。 作为 2030年可持续发展议程。
